		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Can square wave echoes cancel the other wave?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have seen this issue with a few tracks in the game, but it seems to happen randomly, but when it does, it's kinda annoying.
<br />
<br />I like to use the echoing of square waves as it has a nice sound, but don't like that square 2 cancels square 1's sound.
<br />
<br />Can anything be done about this?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
