	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah but if they almost cancel, a very annoying sound is heard. One solution is to use a different duty cycle for the echo, or do what memblers says if your sound engine is complex enough to support that. (when 50% square echoes a 75% or 87.5% rectangle wave it sounds cool).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


