	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Also it's kind of interesting that this phasing effect is present in the hardware, if you hit the sweep registers it automatically adds 1 to the 2nd pulse channel.  The only thing that really shows that effect, that I can think of, is The Guardian Legend - the "alarm sound" before you fight a boss.  It used to sound canceled on emulators before that was discovered.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
